          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The platinum disk containing enriched Te-124(99.3%)",
                "TeO(2) was fitted. The disk was covered with aluminum",
                "foil, 0.25-mm, held down by a clamping plate. An",
                "increase of the disk diameter from 10 mm to 20 mm",
                "increase the surface of the disk four time which",
                "reduces the power densities and allows a much more",
                "effective cooling.",
                "A 10 mm (Te-124) TeO(2) target disk, thickness of",
                " (Te-124)TeO(2)-191-mg/cm**2, was used for target",
                "yields in table 3."
              ]
            }
          ],
